snippet.title: College Football 25 | Gameplay Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Bring Glory Home. Pre-order EA SPORTS College Football 25 today 👉 http://x.ea.com/80401

The CampusIQ gameplay feature set introduces an all-new composure system, player Wear & Tear, screen-shaking homefield advantages and dozens of diverse playstyles across 134 FBS schools. Learn More 👉 http://x.ea.com/80414

In EA SPORTS College Football 25 for PlayStation5 and Xbox Series X|S, experience explosive gameplay variety across 134 FBS schools and immerse yourself in the iconic atmospheres of college football as you chase college greatness.

Introducing the MVP Bundle, including EA SPORTS College Football 25, Madden 25, and bonus rewards to help you make game day every day.  

Subscribe and follow all the EA SPORTS College Football 25 social channels 👉 linktr.ee/easportscollege
